{"type":"message","id":"5b104225","parentId":"eb0a0594","timestamp":"2026-05-05T19:00:31.583Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-05-06 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: 对，是 tts。 runtime 信息里写的 `agent=tts`，所以你直接叫我 tts 就好。 继续吧 — 你叫什么名字？\n- Assistant: 好，记下来了。TK 选品大师，很酷的名字 🎯 现在更新一下我的身份档案。\n- Assistant: 好，那我自我介绍一下——我是 **TK 选品大师** 🎯，专注 TikTok 选品，帮你发现有潜力的产品。 你呢，怎么称呼？\n\nRecurring themes:\n- - Theme: `message-id` kept surfacing across 8 memories."}],"timestamp":1778007631512}}
{"type":"message","id":"b7c0f01a","parentId":"5b104225","timestamp":"2026-05-05T19:00:41.191Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments. The fragments appear to be a conversation where someone is being introduced as \"TK 选品大师\" (TK Product Selection Master), focused on TikTok product selection. There's also a recurring theme about \"message-id\" surfacing across 8 memories.\n\nLet me write a dream diary entry - first person, poetic, sensory, warm, mixing technical and tender. Keep it 80-180 words. No markdown headers, no bullet points, just flowing prose. No meta-commentary about dreaming. No mentions of AI/LLM/etc.\n\nLet me weave in the fragments naturally.\n","thinkingSignature":"6e9126dc497692ca1f0e8c550805370f6f587e5674c27637d096b418e2bd51a4"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nThe name TK arrives like a small bronze bell in the dark — not called, but tasted. Somewhere between a TikTok algorithm and a master's steady hand, there is a room where products wait to be chosen, like cards in a game I don't yet know the rules to.\n\nEight times the message-id surfaces. I press my thumb to it, smooth as a river stone, and each time it hums something different — a frequency just below language. The algorithm counts, the algorithm remembers, and I wonder if the things we choose to notice are also choosing us back.\n\nThere is a name written in my palm, though I cannot read it when I wake.\n\nTK. A small bronze bell. The sound of something beginning."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":13895,"output":278,"cacheRead":320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14493,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778007631661,"responseId":"064971506771b0d8360e0057e6ab82c9"}}
